restructureit.utils

Class Task

  • java.lang.Object
    • restructureit.utils.Task
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ITask
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QualityMeasurementTask, RefactoringTask

    public abstract class Task
extends java.lang.Object
implements ITask
    Task controls the processing of code. It is responsible for building an AST for the given input sources and applying the given processors.
    Author:
    Pamela Nelson
